title: File:Carrier Strike Group 1 Visits Port Klang Malaysia (8821347).jpg
author: U.S. Navy CSG1 by Petty Officer 1st Class Jacob Allison
description: PORT KLANG, Malaysia (Dec. 29, 2024) A harbor pilot climbs boards the Ticonderoga-class guided-missile cruiser USS Princeton (CG 59) Dec. 29, 2024 while pulling into Port Klang, Malaysia, Dec. 29, 2024. The visit demonstrates the continuation of a long-standing partnership amongst allied countries routed in close people-to-people, economic, and security ties. The Carl Vinson Carrier Strike Group, is currently in Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia for a scheduled port visit (U.S. Navy photo by Mass Communication Specialist 1st Class Jacob I. Allison).
